From: Seth Mitchell <smitchell@...
Subject: Level 11

I don't know if anyone else noticed, but the difficulty of level 11
seemed to be harder in version 1.5 than in versions 1.6 and up.  I still
remember playing the demo, and for some reason, my friend and I would
always hide at the bottom left and wall ourselves in with trees so the
enemy couldn't get to us.  Anyone else notice anything like that?
